OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMist and fog locally lingering
OL,6,Funtil late morning. Otherwise, a dry
OL,7,Fday with an increasing amount of
OL,8,Fpleasant spring sunshine developing.
OL,9,FFeeling mild with just a slight breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry this evening and
OL,12,Fovernight with clear spells. Patchy
OL,13,Fmist and fog reforming, though more
OL,14,Fisolated than the previous night.
OL,15,FStrengthening breezes around coasts
OL,16,Fand hills. A cool night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
